        "created_at": "2022-03-27T15:33:17.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p><strong>2019 Vincent Dauvissat (Ren\u00e9 &amp; Vincent) Chablis 1er Cru La Forest</strong></p>\n<p>What a start into the night together with super-fresh langoustine which was a perfect match for this Chablis.  It\u2019s all about balance&amp;harmony, elegance and butterscotch. Very nice acidity too which gives freshness and cellar potential. No doubt 2019 is a terrific vintage, everything is on the right place. I also loved the inner calm in this Chablis. Magnificent wine.<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<img src=\"/uploads/db3686/original/3X/a/3/a3f20a5ec47570af3f0816b2512162205c607580.jpeg\" alt=\"IMG_9365.jpg\" data-base62-sha1=\"nokoCny0QKy1SCzsd5IGdy73rrO\" width=\"2832\" height=\"3953\"></p>",
