        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/j/3d9bf3/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2022-03-27T16:52:49.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>The butterscotch thing gives me pause.</p>\n<p>I also love this producer, but i like this wine with 8-10 years of age, and mine are premoxing by that time.  Plus the price has gotten a little crazy.  I wish they made more of their AC Chablis, which is from similar land near La Forest, and more affordable (although also going way up in price.)  Somewhat hard to find, though.</p>",
