        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/t/258eb7/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2022-03-27T19:01:24.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Forets (alternatively titled La Forest or For\u00eat) is a Premier Cru climat on the western side of the Serein river in Chablis. Located on a south-facing hill of high-quality Kimmeridgian soils just a few miles southwest of Chablis town, For\u00eats produces elegant, steely wines from the Chardonnay grape variety.</p>",
